name: Villa Baru 2
address: BR. BATANDUREN. DESA CEPAKA. KECAMATAN KEDIRI. KABUPATEN TABANAN BALI KODE POST, 94VV+XQ9, Cepaka, Kediri, Tabanan Regency, Bali 82121, Indonesia
review 1: This very beautiful villa in the Cepaka area offers a calm and comfortable natural atmosphere.. this villa offers 3 bedrooms which are very natural in design.. I really recommend it for those of you who want to find a place to stay in Bali because this place is very close to Canggu and other tourist areas.
review 2: Loved our stay in this beautifully renovated villa. Excellent service and very close to many tourist attractions.
review 3: Beatiful villa in a quite Canguu area surrounded by nature.
review 4: Great villa in a beautiful quite village but still very close to the bustle of Canggu. Great service and will definitely come back to stay here again.
review 5: We had a fantastic stay at the villa. Nice quiet area and close to everything. Very friendly landlord who helps with everything.

name: Baru Cafe
address: Jl. Desa Cepaka, Cepaka, Kec. Kediri, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82121, Indonesia
review 1: nice cafe and comfortable atmosphere..highly recommended for those of you who want to enjoy a calm atmosphere..great service
review 2: Nice and cozy coffee place with very friendly staff. Coffee (cappuccino) is good and tasty. They also made is sufficiently hot. Prices are very affordable, good value for money.
review 3: Excellent coffee. Best cappuccino I‚Äôve had in a long time.  The food we ordered from their extensive menu was delicious and great value too.  The staff were very friendly and attentive. Would highly recommend Baru Cafe if you are in the Cepaka area.
review 4: Visited Baru Cafe yesterday & had one of the best coffees in Bali, seriously. It was just about to rain so was thankful to find this lovely little cafe as a sanctuary. Ended up going back a couple of hours later for eggs & bacon on the most delicious sourdough bread. The outlook was so lovely & natural, quite a bit of construction behind it but just a delightful, quiet, cozy space to take some time out with sensational coffee & food. Will be back!
review 5: Amazing Cafe with very delicious food and lovely service. I Love coming here.
